an, and Costello syndromes, which exhibit overlapping phenotypes. A pseudogene of this gene has been identified on the X chromosome. [provided by RefSeq, Aug 2017].","symbol":"BRAF","type_of_gene":"protein-coding","uniprot":{"Swiss-Prot":"P15056","TrEMBL":["H7C560","A0A2U3TZI2","A0A2R8Y8E0","A0A2R8Y679","A0A2R8Y492","H7C4S5","H7C5K3","A0A2R8Y467","A0A2R8YDP5","A0A2R8YES9"]}}]}